Local accounts:
root:UID=0:GID=0 nfsnobody:UID=65534:GID=65534 qemu_base:UID=65535:GID=991 swtpm_base:UID=196608:GID=990 vncterm_base:UID=131072:GID=988

============================================================
--- Assessment Summary ---
STATUS: Open (Finding)
REASON: RBAC infrastructure exists but is not effectively utilized.
  - No external authentication (AD/LDAP) configured.
  - No subjects with differentiated roles (all admin or no subjects).
RECOMMENDATION:
  1. Configure Active Directory integration: xe pool-enable-external-auth
  2. Add subjects with appropriate roles: xe subject-add
  3. Assign least-privilege roles (vm-operator, read-only, etc.)

