					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Rule_Title</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>The VMM must conceal, via the session lock, information previously visible on the display with a publicly viewable image.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
