2. Enable and start: systemctl enable auditd; service auditd start
3. Configure required audit rules in /etc/audit/rules.d/
4. Reload rules: augenrules --load
5. Verify: auditctl -l

Contact the system administrator to configure the audit subsystem.

</COMMENTS>
				<SEVERITY_OVERRIDE />
				<SEVERITY_JUSTIFICATION />
