					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Check_Content</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM checks the validity of all data inputs except those specifically identified by the organization.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
