Audit Tool Access Protection
XCP-ng Version: XCP-ng 8.3.0

  /sbin/auditctl : not found
  /sbin/aureport : not found
  /sbin/ausearch : not found
  /sbin/autrace : not found
  /sbin/auditd : not found
  /sbin/augenrules : not found

