					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM prevents the installation of guest VMs, patches, service packs, device drivers, or VMM components without verification they have been digitally signed using a certificate that is recognized and approved by the organization.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
