					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM to employ a deny-all, permit-by-exception policy to allow the execution of authorized software programs and guest VMs.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
