					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Verify the VMM only allows the use of DoD PKI-established certificate authorities for verification of the establishment of protected sessions.

If it does not, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the VMM to only allow the use of DoD PKI-established certificate authorities for verification of the establishment of protected sessions.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
